  "texts": [
    "By leveraging huge neural architectures, LLMs can organize complex and abstract concepts.",
    "This enables them to identify, translate, predict, and generate new content.",
    "LLMs can be fine-tuned for specific domains (eg, mental health) and enable interactions in natural language, as do many mental health assessments and interventions, highlighting the enormous potential they have to revolutionize mental health care.",
    "In this paper, we first summarize the research done to date applying LLMs to mental health.",
    "Then, we highlight key opportunities and risks associated with mental health LLMs and put forth suggested risk mitigation strategies."
